==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Merrymake
<hw>Mer"ry*make`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Mirth; frolic; a
meeting for mirth; a festival.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>merrimake</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Merrymake</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Merrymake
<hw>Mer"ry*make`</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make merry; to be jolly;
to feast.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>merrimake</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Merrymaker</ent>⟦br⟧
